# Frontend Stack

Mandated libraries — do not substitute alternatives without explicit approval.
Implementation patterns (structure, components, TypeScript) live in `coding-practices.mdc`.

## Styling

- **Tailwind CSS** for all styling — no CSS modules, styled-components, or ad-hoc inline styles.
- Charter colors and typography — see `graphic-chart.mdc`.

## Routing

- **React Router** for client-side navigation.
- Central router in `src/routes/`; use `<Link>` and `useNavigate` for in-app navigation.

## Data Fetching

- **TanStack React Query** for server state (queries, mutations, cache, invalidation).
- API client and query keys in `src/lib/`.

## Forms

- **React Hook Form** for all forms.
- Use `register` or `Controller`; validate with a schema (e.g. Zod).

## UI Feedback

- **React Toastify** — toasts for mutation success and error feedback.
- **React Loader Spinner** — loading indicators tied to query or form pending state.

## React Ecosystem Tools

Use the right library for each UI need — do not reinvent or add duplicates.

| Need | Library | Usage |
|------|---------|-------|
| Icons | React Icons | Import from `react-icons/*`; never inline SVGs for standard icons |
| Pagination | React Pagination | List pages with server-side or client-side paging |
| Select | React Select | Dropdowns with search or multi-select |
| Date | React Datepicker | Date fields in forms |
| Time | React Timepicker | Time fields in forms |

Wrap third-party components in a local UI primitive when used in more than one place (e.g. `components/ui/Select.tsx` around React Select).

## Checklist When Adding a Feature

- [ ] Route added in central router
- [ ] Data fetched via React Query with loading / error / empty states
- [ ] Forms use React Hook Form
- [ ] Icons from React Icons; dates/times/selects from the table above
- [ ] Feedback via Toastify and Loader Spinner
